From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 01:49:22 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Optimize fluid tick scheduling

Add a Fand-gated fluid tick container priority queue so fluid ticks do not scan every loaded tick container each server tick.

Keep vanilla tick execution and ordering intact while retrying blocked chunks on the next tick instead of requeueing them into the same due set, preventing watchdog spins when tickCheck is false.

Add a fixed-array FlowingFluid spread path to avoid per-tick EnumMap allocation, and pass block placement item context into Fand placement events.

